					</image>
				</p>

				<p>
					Using the sign chart, we an read off the behavior of the function. 
					<m>f</m> is <em>increasing</em> on the interval <m>(8,\infty)</m>, and <m>f</m> is <em>decreasing</em> on the interval <m>(-\infty,0)\cup(0,8)</m>
				</p>
				<p>
					We can also see that <m>f</m> has a local maxima at <m>x=8</m>, but <m>f</m> has <em>no</em> local minima (the local minima <m>DNE</m>).
				</p>
			</solution>
		</task>
		<task>
			<statement>
